header: Test vectors of type DsaP1363Verify are meant for the verification
of IEEE P1363 encoded DSA signatures.

notes.EdgeCase: Some implementations of DSA do not properly check for boundaries. In some cases the modular inverse of 0 is simply 0. As a result there are implementations where values such as r=1, s=0 lead to forgeries.
